title: Depeche Mode 12Inch Vinyl DVDAudio 24bit_96kHz
description:
This is a transfer of 12" Maxi-single Vinyl records that I have with Depeche Mode.

Sampling and DVD-Audio recording has been done in 24bit/96kHz.

Note! This is a DVD-Audio recording and it requires a DVD-Audio compatible player. A DVD-Video only player won&#039;t do.
